# UIDropSessionProgressIndicatorStyle.none

**Case**

The indicator style for no drop-progress indication.

## Declaration

```swift
case none
```

## Progress indicator styles

- **UIDropSessionProgressIndicatorStyle.default**: The indicator style for using the system’s default drop-progress indication.
